body.section:
This procedure should be applied when the following error is received when installing a
           Microsoft SQL 2012/2014 service.
            [general] Unable to attach broker to cluster: Received a status code 504 Gateway Time-out {
       "code": 10001,
       "description": "The request to the service broker timed out: http://192.168.15.123:3000/v2/catalog",
       "error_code": "CF-ServiceBrokerApiTimeout",
       "http": {
         "uri": "http://192.168.15.123:3000/v2/catalog",
         "method": "GET"
       }
     }This
           procedure will also repair Microsoft SQL nodes which are in a degraded status.
